metadata.name: Zoomer mfers 3Deeze I - déjà vu
metadata.description:
"Zoomer mfers 3Deeze I - déjà vu" is AI art 'seeded' from an original oil painting by DHW; includes additional creative processes by the artist. No text to image processes were used.

This piece is an extension of "Zoomer mfers 3Deeze I", hence the déjà vu. Like the original piece, this extended version relates to the poor environmental state that zoomers and subsequent generations will inherit.
